{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><em><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name\"><code>name</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></strong> コンストラクタは新しい <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a> を作成し、それを基礎となるチャネルに接続します。</p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>注:</strong> この機能は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 内で利用可能です</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"> channel = new BroadcastChannel(channel);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"値","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"channel\"><em>channel</em></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>チャネルの名前を表す <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> です。 同じ<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Origin\">オリジン</a>を持つすべての<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Browsing_context\">閲覧コンテキスト</a>に対して、この名前を持つ単一のチャンネルがあります。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// \"internal_notification\" チャンネルをリッスンする新しいチャンネルを作成します。</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'internal_notification'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nbc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'New listening connected!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"仕様","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>仕様</th>\n      <th>状態</th>\n      <th>コメント</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/comms.html#dom-broadcastchannel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">BroadcastChannel() の定義</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n      <td>初期定義</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.BroadcastChannel","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"i